        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Get 2hs for the level 12 pet. It will nullify the magic attack, but will dish out loads more dmg to those mobs that don't need magic to be hit.</P><P>Go kill sisters on the sister isle in OOT; they drop some neat halbeards for your pet. Later on though, weapons won't help pet do more dmg. only good if you get some Gnoll Hide Lariats to proc that stun.</P><P>WTB Gnoll Hide Lariats</P><P>*EDIT* Yes, Gnoll Hide Lariats was an example. Just get your pet anything that procs.. like that ranger dagger that procs a 600dd!!!</P><P>Vermis Mysteriis<BR>55 defiler of Torvonnilous</P><P>Edited by - Vermis Mysteriis on 11/05/2001  02:23:12<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
