        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">The level 12 pet can actually be level 12 itself, so if you are leel 12, then it should con white to you.<BR>Untill your pet can dual wield, then the 2H weapons will be best.<BR>When it can dual wield, then get a few rusty long swords.<BR>When you get your level 34 then forget about no-proccing weapons.<BR>The delay on pets are fixed to 30, so weapons with high delays will be lowered to 30. :)</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
